divs: Sighting Details4 objects where seen my me and my passenger, (name deleted)fg, approximately at mile marker 26 heading north on I-55. These object were flying slow over the interstate. One oject was away from the other three. Two objects where flying parallel and close to each other and the other object was making curves in flight, while flying with the other three objects. Other cars noticed these objects and the rate of traffic slowed. I am an airplane nut and noticed there where no red and blue or white lights, nor did I see any strob lights blinking on the objects. And no sound came from the objects as my window was down. These objects where auburn in color.
